519
00:41:04,850 --> 00:41:06,360
Sealed in.

520
00:41:06,370 --> 00:41:08,650
Re-routed the blast.

521
00:41:09,220 --> 00:41:11,520
I couldn't save him.

522
00:41:14,750 --> 00:41:17,910
Tosh? There you go, darling.

523
00:41:21,590 --> 00:41:24,580
