animals on the streets of the city.

527
00:42:41,630 --> 00:42:43,800
My whole life I was looking for him.

528
00:42:43,810 --> 00:42:45,940
Now I have to lose him all over again.

529
00:42:45,950 --> 00:42:47,510
You cryo-freeze him and then what?

530
00:42:47,520 --> 00:42:50,170
Wake him up in a 100 years
and he's miraculously better?

531
00:42:50,180 --> 00:42:52,400
Cos that's not gonna happen.

532
00:42:52,410 --> 00:42:55,410
Maybe killing him would
be the release he needs.

533
00:42:55,430 --> 00:42:58,670
There has been enough death.

534
00:43:01,140 --> 00:43:03,460
You didn't struggle...

535
00:43:03,470 --> 00:43:05,330
