540
00:44:01,160 --> 00:44:03,200
Lot of this planet I haven't seen.

541
00:44:03,210 --> 00:44:05,430
You like it so much, thought
I might take a look.

542
00:44:05,440 --> 00:44:07,690
Maybe see you around.

543
00:44:12,410 --> 00:44:16,140
I'm sorry for your losses.

544
00:44:55,540 --> 00:44:58,930
