546
00:45:47,000 --> 00:45:49,890
OK. So...

547
00:45:50,350 --> 00:45:55,110
if you're seeing this, I guess
it means, I'm... well, dead.

548
00:45:55,930 --> 00:45:57,640
Hope it was impressive!

549
00:45:57,650 --> 00:46:00,920
Not crossing the road or
an incident with a toaster.

550
00:46:02,210 --> 00:46:04,680
I just wanted to say...

551
00:46:04,690 --> 00:46:06,790
it's OK.

552
00:46:06,800 --> 00:46:09,360
It really is.

553
00:46:09,920 --> 00:46:13,410
Jack, you saved me.

554
00:46:14,100 --> 00:46:17,620
You showed me all the
wonders of the universe and...

555
00:46:17,630 --> 00:46:20,320
all those possibilities.

556
00:46:20,330 --> 00:46:23,120
And I wouldn't have
missed it for the world.

557
00:46:23,600 --> 00:46:25,680
Thank you.

558
00:46:26,610 --> 00:46:31,190
And Owen, you never knew.

559
00:46:34,600 --> 00:46:38,360
I love you. All of you.

560
00:46:38,810 --> 00:46:41,230
And...

561
00:46:41,590 --> 00:46:44,470
I hope I did good.

562
00:46:54,750 --> 00:46:57,510
Now we carry on.

